### Get all expenses
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get expenses by month, year, and category
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?month=6&year=2026&category=Rent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get expenses by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?startDate=2026-06-01&endDate=2026-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create expense
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Salary",
  "amount": 10000,
  "description": "Guard was unpaid. Cleared his salary",
  "expenseDate": "2026-06-05"
}

### Update expense
PUT {{baseUrl}}/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 43000,
  "description": "June showroom rent with maintenance"
}

### Delete expense
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
